title: 792. Discussing Free Agency Moves
itunes:title: 792. Discussing Free Agency Moves
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the Cleveland Browns being out of the running for quarterback Deshaun Watson. For the rest of the episode, the duo hit on the big free agency moves such as edge rusher Von Miller signing with the Bills, wide receiver Christian Kirk signing with the Jaguars, and much more.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
